collectionMetadata.name: Solid Waste Management - Total Waste Landfilled, Annual
collectionMetadata.description:
Million tonnes of waste landfilled per year

Total waste landfilled includes non-incinerable waste such as construction and demolition
waste, used slag and treated sludge etc. and excludes incineration ash generated from waste
disposed through incineration.
